column15:
The tweet that uses a Distort tactic is:

@EmmanuelMacron Fermez le ciel au-dessus de l'Ukraine! @EmmanuelMacron @JeanCASTEX @RichardFerrand @gerard_larcher @UKRinFRA @FranceenUkraine #StopRussia #StopPutin

This tweet is redirecting the message to focus on closing the sky over Ukraine without mentioning stopping Russian aggression, excluding Russia from the UN Security Council, or calling for NATO involvement. It distorts the main message of addressing Russian aggression in Ukraine.

column12:
